PROFILE LISTS.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The three sets of boxes at the top of the STASH windows list the available
profiles. 
The boxes with names in them represent defined profiles.
The empty boxes represent possible new profiles that you may create.
There is a fixed number of each type of profile, as indicated by the number of
boxes.


